column5: Test your reflexes Try out this game.  Shoot the sheep with a tranquilizer dart as soon as they run. The game records your reaction time, and gives you an average time out of 5 tries. The best average I could get was .168  http://www.bbc.co.uk/science/humanbody/sleep/sheep/
My .248 means I had a "good beer day" then I guess...

lol, i actually got one at 0.0000 ... never gonna get that again. I didn't know how it work for the first 2, and on the 3rd one i finally knew i had to press that thing ... must have gotten too excited and it just so happened it ran out ...

o.o66. Faster reaction times come from keeping finger on trigger. Most people have a habit of removing the finger from the trigger which adds atravel time of 1/10 to 2/10ths  of a second.  Gets addictive. Had to go back until I got a better time.  0.016
.276... no wonder i miss the fish... it even said I should have a coffee...( no crap batman,.,, i haven't had one yet..)  LOL
0.159  with one at 0.000 seconds as well. haha
.188 was as good as I could get...my finger started twitching!
